{"tid":2121203,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"八達通有員工確診新型肺炎　客戶熱線等服務或受影響","createTime":"2020-07-23T07:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T07:21:25.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ecddf600674ac653512963d5413fa5f4c610d3aa","tid":2121203,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:18:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539434-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539434-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=QJrJoCvBX0rL8AB4Pa6kCBzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=fee5e004\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539434-20200723.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=79724ff7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539434-20200723.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n八達通公司證實一名在九龍灣總部上班的員工確診感染新型肺炎，目前情況穩定，正等候安排送院。公司部分運作，如客戶服務熱線或會受影響。<br />\n<br />\n八達通公司表示，確診員工在46樓上班，最後上班日期為上星期五，並未與其他同事於工作上有密切接觸，工作時亦一直有佩戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n公司已立即安排同一樓層的同事撤離辦公室，並正安排徹底清潔及消毒相關樓層和所有公共範圍，該樓層的員工已獲通知暫時不應返回辦公室，直至另行通知。"},{"pid":"8cbf7772c8497688bcc6624b1e2265988f00579d","tid":2121203,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-23T07:21:25.000Z","msg":"好黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}